### Movie Ticket Booking — runnable API walkthrough
### Open in IntelliJ (or VS Code REST Client) and run the requests top to bottom.
### Start the app first:  ./mvnw spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=demo

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Log in as the seeded admin (captures the admin token)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@moviebooking.com", "password": "admin123" }

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.token); %}

### 2. Register a customer (captures the customer token)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "customer@example.com", "password": "secret123", "fullName": "Test Customer" }

> {% client.global.set("customerToken", response.body.token); %}

### 3. Browse movies (public)
GET {{host}}/api/movies

### 4. Shows for movie 1 (public)
GET {{host}}/api/movies/1/shows

### 5. Seat map for show 1 (public) — pick showSeatIds from the response
GET {{host}}/api/shows/1/seats

### 6. Hold seats 1 and 2 for show 1 (captures the hold id)
POST {{host}}/api/holds
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{ "showId": 1, "showSeatIds": [1, 2] }

> {% client.global.set("holdId", response.body.holdId); %}

### 7. Confirm the booking (captures the booking id)
POST {{host}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{ "holdId": {{holdId}} }

> {% client.global.set("bookingId", response.body.id); %}

### 8. Booking history
GET {{host}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 9. Notifications (confirmation appears here)
GET {{host}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 10. Cancel the booking (refund per policy)
DELETE {{host}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### --- Admin examples ---

### Create a city
POST {{host}}/api/admin/cities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "name": "Mumbai" }

### Create a discount code
POST {{host}}/api/admin/discount-codes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "code": "SAVE10", "type": "PERCENT", "amount": 10, "minAmount": 100, "maxUses": 100 }

### Preview a discount (any logged-in user)
POST {{host}}/api/discounts/preview
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

{ "code": "SAVE10", "subtotal": 1000 }

### Change the premium seat multiplier
PUT {{host}}/api/admin/pricing-tiers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "code": "SEAT_PREMIUM", "description": "Premium seat", "multiplier": 1.75 }

### Change a refund tier
PUT {{host}}/api/admin/refund-policies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "minHoursBeforeShow": 2, "refundPercent": 60 }
